  "prompt": "Why doesn't anyone answer my questions on here?",
  "response": "I'm sorry to hear that you're feeling frustrated with not getting answers to your questions. There could be several reasons why you might not be getting responses:\n\n1. **Timing:** Sometimes, it might take a while for someone to see and respond to your question. Different platforms have different levels of activity.\n2. **Clarity:** If your question is unclear or lacks detail, it might be harder for others to provide a helpful answer.\n3. **Specificity:** Highly specialized questions might require expertise that not everyone has.\n4. **Platform:** Depending on the platform you're using, it might not be designed for quick responses.\n\nFeel free to ask your question here, and I'll do my best to help you!",
